# Extraction quality benchmark fixtures must compare byte-equal across platforms.
# Pin LF line endings so Windows checkouts don't rewrite expected.md / input.html
# on `git checkout` (autocrlf default). The benchmark's ReplaceLineEndings("\n")
# handles in-memory normalisation, but consistent-on-disk avoids ambiguity.
* text eol=lf
*.md text eol=lf
*.html text eol=lf
